<style type="text/css">
p{
color:red; or color:#ff0000; or color:rgb(0,0,255); or color: rgb(128,255,255);
}
</style>

NOTE:
1. 
#ff0000 => This 6 digit is an hexadecimal number, ff placed at first 2 position stands for red color, 
#ff0000 => red
#00ff00 => green
#0000ff => blue

2.
rgb stands for red, green, blue where 255 is the maximum value for blue color and as we don't need red and green first and second parameters are 0. 
